{"tid":2207083,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[小陽春初現] 沙田第一城2房 呎價重上1.93萬","createTime":"2020-09-18T02:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T03:13:40.000Z","uid":316048,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"045f10dc1dedb4f8fb4101d95dbae9217aeb656b","tid":2207083,"uid":316048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:57:42.000Z","msg":"大型上車屋苑沙田第一城二手成交氣氛回暖，價錢亦有稍有回升的情況，實用面積284平方呎2房單位呎價重上1.9萬水平。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產沙田第一城分區營業經理侯惠良表示，近日二手交投氣氛正面，不少買家加快入市步伐。沙田第一城最新錄得成交單位為38座中層B室，建築面積395平方呎，實用面積284平方呎，2房間隔，議價後以550萬元易手，實用平均呎價19366元。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，原業主則於2014年以326萬元購入單位，持貨6年，是次沽出單位獲利224萬元離場，單位升值約68.7%。<br />\n<br />\n疫情減退少少香港人已經開始搶樓， 一開埋關真係唔敢想像 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237777b6e3d851f29fb9fdffb4ba1bbc053a963d","tid":2207083,"uid":2429,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:59:32.000Z","msg":"賣樓正傻閪。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b825f6b20cf779d5168816cce85269a5ece95a8d","tid":2207083,"uid":61882,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"小乜楊乜春吖<br />\n明顯係迴光返照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808f2ea041a2a66233b50617f43bd8dbadb417fa","tid":2207083,"uid":248578,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"284呢隻2房呎價一向貴<br />\n沙一284, 304, 327 2房一向睇lump sum唔睇呎價<br />\n高位成600-620萬<br />\n550都講緊仲係跌左10%"},{"pid":"2e2fa6960668b67cd45c441ec841d31d469c6720","tid":2207083,"uid":267488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"樓市gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a511a312ed167a95d2a51c08fe95cf04c33c1d","tid":2207083,"uid":235727,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"808f2ea041